{"tid":386211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加國華裔議員　聲援港年輕抗爭者","createTime":"2017-09-03T16:53:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T12:16:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e391ac587aff6ffe0d1a3b3f5d3f2728708394b4","tid":386211,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:53:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170903/20141010\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170903%2F20141010&d=d1%2FAf9e1WbMxd7nKXcPtMcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=0b9805d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170903%2F20141010&h=3c9a7f15\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170903/20141010</a><br />\n<br />\n加國華裔議員　聲援港年輕抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n14,885<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170903/large/a0205a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170903%2Flarge%2Fa0205a.gif&h=f0a73886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■加拿大華裔國會議員關慧貞<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】剛訪問中國和香港的加拿大華裔國會議員關慧貞，發聲明支援因律政司司長袁國強覆核刑期而被判監的16人。她讚揚香港年輕人的勇氣，以及他們非暴力的行動令她深受啟發；又透露曾與包括加拿大駐港總領事在內各界人士討論本港近期發展，他們均對情況感憂慮。關敦促港府與其壓制這些聲音，更應想想為何公眾會提出這些問題。<br />\n<br />\n在香港出生的關慧貞指出，2014年雨傘運動是「一場為香港爭取民主和更具問責政府的社會運動」，對於包括黃之鋒在內的雙學三子及反新界東北案等被告，因袁國強提覆核刑期而被判監，關對此表示十分失望，而他們其實已完成原審判決刑罰。<br />\n<br />\n對港政局發展感憂慮<br />\n<br />\n此案也令人擔心會對港人和平請願及言論自由造成寒蟬效應，質疑背後有政治動機和幕後操縱，強調港府與其壓制這些聲音和提問，反而應好好地想，為何公眾會提出這些問題，以及為何這樣的情緒會在上升。<br />\n<br />\n關亦提到，訪港期間與包括加拿大駐港總領事Jeff Nankivell在內的政治觀察人士談論香港政局，他們均對近期本港發展感憂慮，她指港府不應以加重刑罰來回應港人對民主和表達自由的訴求。<br />\n<br />\n■記者呂浩然  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n譚允芝撐上訴庭　轟外媒未研判詞<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n戴耀廷　陳澤滔列人大選民名單"},{"pid":"63fbf50285afd367f45e314d0148ebb9161b8820","tid":386211,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:57:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a22d28bdf14ecc55d3db55df0e58edccb58aae12","tid":386211,"uid":35236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:59:07.000Z","msg":"係就出手做野啦<br />\n個個都得把口<br />\n屌"},{"pid":"bd8aaf5f98f7dd68fe4e2511e3472a031e4020f6","tid":386211,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:59:21.000Z","msg":"慧貞"},{"pid":"d3e3e35eca7d596fbb9a56a0a8bc5e182a86c709","tid":386211,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T21:16:53.000Z","msg":"佢噉都係「華裔」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大中華膠真係咩都可以「被華人」"},{"pid":"f9d4354d58384ddebcf7b07dfb8f2979c38c9fc2","tid":386211,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T21:19:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係就出手做野啦<br />\n個個都得把口<br />\n屌</blockquote><br />\n等你班友打下飛機開心下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec63dc97f6d2eb33e761dfdc39c7acbc39bf0491","tid":386211,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T00:53:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢噉都係「華裔」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大中華膠真係咩都可以「被華人」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nwhy not ?<br />\n種族冇得變 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"861a71bd2f5a82329f9b70a27da1edffdd2549c7","tid":386211,"uid":476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T01:14:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢噉都係「華裔」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大中華膠真係咩都可以「被華人」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nwhy not ?<br />\n種族冇得變 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老豆老母都港人 9歲移民 會變白人鬼婆？"},{"pid":"e0cd8117e4373592ffe0fc2ed1d3e9cf938e814a","tid":386211,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T01:16:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢噉都係「華裔」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大中華膠真係咩都可以「被華人」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nwhy not ?<br />\n種族冇得變 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老豆老母都港人 9歲移民 會變白人鬼婆？</blockquote><br />\n遲下將日本人韓國人都變埋支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0913c7b08a7dc175f3d97ec20660f1243251fe9e","tid":386211,"uid":18271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T01:22:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢噉都係「華裔」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大中華膠真係咩都可以「被華人」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%97%9C%E6%85%A7%E8%B2%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2585%25A7%25E8%25B2%259E&d=d1%2FAf9e1WbMxd7nKXcPtMcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=3d038801\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%97%9C%E6%85%A7%E8%B2%9E</a><br />\n<br />\n關慧貞生於香港，9歲時跟隨家人移民加拿大卑詩省溫哥華，能說流利的廣東話和英文。她畢業於西門菲沙大學，主修犯罪學[1]。<br />\n<br />\n關氏現與丈夫、女兒、兒子和繼子在溫哥華東區居住[1]。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不如縮返入你老母個閪度啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018c6a20636cf31138437e47692942e834a59880","tid":386211,"uid":59